data.description:
BRING AN OFFER!! Welcome to your dream family home nestled in the sought-after Stoneridge Farms Addition. This beautifully designed 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home is perfect for family and hosting. With an upstairs living room, open living spaces, Jack n Jill secondary rooms, tornado shelter, a prime location within walking distance to Stoneridge Elementary and the community pool, this home is a true gem. You have access to the turnpike within minutes for all of your shopping, entertainment, and restaurants. Contact listing agent for a private showing before this home is GONE.

Rent to own available with only 7% DOWN!!
